snippet.title: Alt-G: A Lateral Thinking Game for Android (trailer)
snippet.description:
Alt-G is a truly original brain teasers game for Android.
Play with your hands, face, voice and more.
Ridiculous solutions that will push you to think outside of the box.
Free on Google Play now.
Enjoy and have fun!
